'''Tasewlent''' d yiwet seg talɣiwin n [[alɣas|ulɣas]] ɣer [[aɣersiw|yiɣersiwen]], yemmug am [[tasegrest|tsegrest]] - maca iḍerr-d deg [[anebdu|unebdu]], s tenmegla n taegrest i d-iḍerrun deg [[tagrest|tegrest]] -. Igellu-d s tdersi n wermud n iɣersiwen. Tettili-d tsewlent deg tfadiwin n [[taẓɣelt|teẓɣelt]] d [[anaɣur|unaɣur]], anda ikeččmen iɣersiwen [[Tinaɣlalin|inaɣlalen]] d [[Tiraɣlalin|iraɣlalen]] deg waddad n [[anuddem|unuddem]] i wakken ad ssanfel tikewt.

